    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 改变了游戏规则：华尔街专家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/deepseek-is-a-gamechanger-wall-street-experts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周华尔街开局不利，因为人们担心中国初创公司 DeepSeek 推出的廉价人工智能模型可能威胁美国科技公司的主导地位。彭博电视台的嘉宾就市场反应以及这将如何影响白宫政策发表了看法。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/deepseek-is-a-gamechanger-wall-street-experts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 19:12:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Katam Hill 谈对 Nvidia 的期望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/katam-hill-s-gold-on-what-to-expect-from-nvidia-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Katam Hill LLC 创始人兼首席信息官 Adam Gold 讨论了 DeepSeek 科技股的抛售及其对 Nvidia 的影响。他在“彭博市场”节目中与 Scarlet Fu 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/katam-hill-s-gold-on-what-to-expect-from-nvidia-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 19:08:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 引发对 AI 底层竞争的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/deepseek-sparks-race-to-the-ai-bottom-fears-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 DeepSeek 的 AI 潜力席卷科技市场，T. Rowe Price 投资组合经理兼 Nvidia 重要股东 Tony Wang 表示，该公司的开源模式有利于创新和 AI 社区。他与 Caroline Hyde 和 Mike Shepard 一起在“彭博科技”节目中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/deepseek-sparks-race-to-the-ai-bottom-fears-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 19:08:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek Tech 的抛售情况如何？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/what-is-happening-with-deepseek-tech-selloff-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DeepSeek 引发科技股抛售，但该公司似乎突然崛起。彭博社的 Rachel Metz 解释了 DeepSeek 以及科技行业正在发生的事情。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/what-is-happening-with-deepseek-tech-selloff-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 18:31:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 AI 赌注为 X Debt 注入了 60 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/x-debt-shopped-with-6b-sweetener-from-musk-s-ai-bet-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 xAI Corp. Sridhar Natarajan 报道，华尔街银行正准备出售与伊隆·马斯克收购 X（前身为 Twitter）相关的价值 30 亿美元的优先担保债务，同时附加对 X 在马斯克人工智能合资企业中的股份的索取权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-27/x-debt-shopped-with-6b-sweetener-from-musk-s-ai-bet-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 18:18:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着杠杆押注暴跌，Nvidia-ETF 组合面临关键时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/nvidia-etf-complex-faces-moment-of-truth-as-levered-bets-plunge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，日内交易员投入了数十亿美元购买 Nvidia Corp. 的杠杆 ETF，以期从这只全球最热门的股票上获得更大的收益。现在，这些赌注岌岌可危。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/nvidia-etf-complex-faces-moment-of-truth-as-levered-bets-plunge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 18:07:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股暴跌助长避险买盘，美国债券收益率跌至今年最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/us-yields-slide-to-three-week-low-as-tech-risk-fuels-haven-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在科技股引发的抛售潮导致股市暴跌后，投资者纷纷涌向安全的美国政府债券，导致美国国债价格周一上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/us-yields-slide-to-three-week-low-as-tech-risk-fuels-haven-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 09:34:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 5600 亿美元 DeepSeek 惨败，创市场历史上最大惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/asml-sinks-as-china-ai-startup-triggers-panic-in-tech-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受投资者对中国人工智能初创企业 DeepSeek 的担忧影响，英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 股价暴跌，导致这家全球最大公司的市值蒸发创纪录水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/asml-sinks-as-china-ai-startup-triggers-panic-in-tech-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 08:18:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员预计特朗普将选择关税而非制裁，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场普遍存在避险情绪，且人们越来越一致认为特朗普政府的贸易和外交政策将更多地依赖关税，而非限制供应的制裁，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 23:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芯片制造商遭遇 2020 年以来最严重崩盘，股市受创：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，华尔街开局并不顺利，因为人们担心中国初创公司 DeepSeek 的廉价人工智能模型可能会让推动牛市的技术的估值变得难以合理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 22:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
